<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Easy Brownies</h1>
    <img src="https://www.kingarthurbaking.com/sites/default/files/styles/featured_image/public/recipe_legacy/1228-3-large.jpg?itok=ADPr9QfO" alt="Brownies">

    <section>
        <h2>Ingredients</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>½ cup (115g) unsalted butter</li>
            <li>1 cup (200g) granulated sugar</li>
            <li>2 large eggs</li>
            <li>1 teaspoon vanilla extract</li>
            <li>⅓ cup (40g) unsweetened cocoa powder</li>
            <li>½ cup (65g) all-purpose flour</li>
            <li>¼ teaspoon salt</li>
            <li>¼ teaspoon baking powder</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Instructions</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Melt ½ cup butter.</li>
            <li>Mix in 1 cup sugar, 2 eggs, 1 tsp vanilla.</li>
            <li>Stir in ⅓ cup cocoa, ½ cup flour, pinch salt, ¼ tsp baking powder.</li>
            <li>Pour into a greased 8x8 pan.</li>
            <li>Bake at 350°F (175°C) for ~20–25 min.</li>
        </ol>
    </section>

    <footer>Cool and Enjoy Your Brownies!</footer>
</div>
